Package: sqlhelpers
Type: Package
Title: Helper functions for querying Sql Databases
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Tom Jemmett
Maintainer: Tom Jemmett <tom.jemmett@gmail.com>
Description: Functions to help users query data from Sql databases in a simple
    and safe manor, handling the opening and closing of connections,
    parameterisation of queries and reading .sql files, utilising odbc to
    connect to servers.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    readr,
    DBI,
    odbc,
    tibble,
    lubridate,
    purrr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
